examples.en: Shops, houses, and vehicles were set ablaze.
examples.ru: Магазины, дома и автомобили были подожжены.

examples.en: His face was ablaze with excitement.
His eyes were ablaze with fury.
In spring, the valleys are ablaze with colour.
Within minutes the whole house was ablaze.
examples.ru: Не прошло и нескольких минут, как весь дом был охвачен пламенем.

examples.en: His face all ablaze with excitement.
examples.ru: Всё его лицо пылало от возбуждения.

examples.en: The factory had been set ablaze (=made to burn).
Her yard was ablaze with summer flowers.
